Formatting purpose filters in angularjs


{{ expression | uppercase }}

uppercase -- to format into capital letters.

lowercase

currency -- convert number value into currency format.

			default currency symbol is $.
			
			we can change by providing indian rupee symbol.
			
I want to apply client side pagination we use limitTo

it is expecting 2 parameters

1 --> size 

2 --> starting index of the collection.



