user input --> filter data

filter filter need work with group of values

<input type="text" name="sname" ng-model="studentName"/>

ng-repeat = "name in names | filter:studentName"

data binding is used provide dynamic values. these values will be provided by user.

input --> studentName --> filter --> names  | user

Limit TO:-

	to display a set of records from the array.
	
